Class MessageFieldSpec

  • java.lang.Object
    • protopoet.MessageFieldSpec
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Buildable<MessageField>, MessageField, Useable.Field

    public final class MessageFieldSpec
extends java.lang.Object
implements MessageField, Useable.Field
    Defines a field for use with MessageSpec. Learn more: https://developers.google.com/protocol-buffers/docs/reference/proto3-spec#message_definition
